headline: Super Micro Computer’s AI Surge Raises Questions On Value And Durability
summary: Super Micro Computer reported record quarterly results, supported by strong demand for AI focused server and storage platforms. Management raised full year guidance and highlighted an expanding manufacturing footprint to support global AI buildouts. headline: 2 Services Stocks on Our Buy List and 1 We Ignore
summary: Business services providers thrive by solving complex operational challenges for their clients, allowing them to focus on their secret sauce. But cutbacks in corporate spending and the threat of new AI products have kept sentiment in check, and over the past six months, the industry’s 3.8% return has trailed the S&P 500 by 4.6 percentage points.
